      "formatId": "note",
      "relation": "All legacy Office formats (.doc, .xls, .ppt, .msg, .pub, .mpp) share the OLE2/CFB container — same 8-byte magic. Distinction by root CLSID or stream names. Replaced by OOXML formats (.docx, .xlsx, .pptx) from Office 2007 onward.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
